      <p>
  The Genesys Care Log File Masking Utility is a standalone version of the data scrubbing function in the Log File Management Tool.  
  This utility is meant for users who have not had the benefit of downloading and installing our Log File Management Tool (LFMT).
  It serves the important need of sanitizing sensitive information from log files before they are sent to Customer Care for support case investigation.
   </p>
<p>
<br/>
In addition, the Log File Masking Utility provides:
<ul>
    <li>Robust scrubbing when multiple regular expressions are defined
    </li>
    <li>The ability to scrub multiple entries from a single line in a log file with one regular expression
    </li>
</ul>
</p><br/>

